headline: Three Reasons to Avoid TTWO and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Take-Two has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 7.2%. The stock now trades at $190.46, marking a 19.3% gain. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
